                                                     THE LIST OF GAMES I HAVE PLAYED. (list for my future son)
                                                     
RED DEAD REDEMPTION 2 [LEGEND-BEST GAME OF ALL TIME FOR ME] (Story, long play-time, amazing-detailed game)
THE LAST OF US PART 1 [LEGEND] (Joel and Ellie relation)
GOD OF WAR [LEGEND:θρύλος] (Amazing action-story game, I love no cutscenes, one camera game.)
GOD OF WAR RAGNAROK [LEGEND] (Amazing story and action)
Marvel's Spider-Man 2 [LEGEND] (Amazingly connected story and action, long play-time)
BLACK MYTH WUKONG [LEGEND] (The thing kept me playing- action, hitting with jingu-bang)
DETROIT: BECOME HUMAN [LEGEND] (MACHINE OR LIVING BEING, every choice you make shapes story)
GHOSTRUNNER [LEGEND] (I love that you need to be fast, agile. Also the story is awesome)
GHOSTRUNNER 2 [LEGEND] (Slash enemies and enjoy story, I especially loved Rahu)
Marvel's Spider-Man [LEGEND, BEST SPIDER-MAN GAME-actually second one is best] (Swinging and action)
Uncharted 4: A Thief's End [LEGEND]
WITCHER 3 [LEGEND] (Best RPG game for me. I stick to Yennefer :D)
BATTLEFIELD 1 [LEGEND]
Ghost of Tsushima [GOOD] (Cutting enemies with katana is awesome, good story but hated the black screen between scenes)
STAR WARS JEDI SURVIVOR [GOOD]
Horizon Zero Dawn [SUPER]
Cyberpunk 2077 [SUPER] (Keanu Reeves)
Mafia Definitive Edition [GOOD] (Good story, but very slow game)
BEYOND TWO SOULS [LEGEND]
Deathloop [GOOD IDEA But SHIT ending]
Call Of Duty Black Ops 1,2 [LEGEND]
Call Of Duty Black Ops Cold War [Normal]
Call Of Duty Modern Warfare 1,2,3 [LEGEND]
Marvels Spider Man Miles Morales [GOOD. Good swinging, fighting, action. But story was very short and not that good]
Mortal Kombat 11 [SUPER]
Control [mediocre]
Metro Exodus [Half played, dont remember why, maybe not impressed]
Dying Light 2 [doing same things. bored-half played]
Death Stranding [good graphics but not impressed, too much task stuff]
Elden Ring [good graphics but very hard. don't have that much time to grind in this game]
